    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like the game please don't forget to add it to your wishlist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1759159519\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1759159519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1759159519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wendigo Hunter</strong> is an action roguelite dungeon crawler with mysterious atmosphere and minimalistic visual. As a chosen member of a cult you will try to hunt down a mythological creature hiding deep in dungeons and abandoned ruins. Unleash a captivating journey where fallen enemies' souls become the key to unlocking mesmerizing magical skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight, collect, upgrade, die, try again...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/d254dd60f2182cf603996f5661c9ad0e.poster.avif?t=1759159519\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/d254dd60f2182cf603996f5661c9ad0e.webm?t=1759159519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/d254dd60f2182cf603996f5661c9ad0e.mp4?t=1759159519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > master your fighting skills in combat with various creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > explore randomly generated dungeon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > upgrade your magical skills by collecting souls of dead enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > gain permanent upgrades by spending collected gems</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you succeed or the next hunter from the cult will need to be chosen?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT DEVELOPER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peter Jurkovský, solo developer and father of 1, began work on Wendigo Hunter as a hobby in 2022 after releasing his first PC game called Juro Janosik.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/377010ce2c5301c068517e5a59c65ac5.avif?t=1759159519\" width=194 height=91 /></span>* Supported using public funding by Slovak Arts Council</p>",
